                    <span>I've studied the works of Dr. King since I was 7 years old, and now my 7 year old is studying him with great interest.  I figured this book (a gift) would be a good summation of his career instead of the other half dozen individual books I have in my library.  Well, as with his other work, there are many, many typographical errors.  I feel that a man of his education would be offended to see his works corroded by half-assed spell checking.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Every American should read this book</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>3</span>
                      /
                      <span>3</span>
                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
